        Selling Vacant Land in Brisbane: How the Process and Market Differ from Selling a Home
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A vacant block sells to a narrower buyer pool, on a different contract, with a different marketing pack and a different set of tax consequences than a house. Here is how Brisbane sellers should prepare.
      </p>
